<div class="container mt-3">
    <h1 class="text-light pixel-font text-center">Listen</h1>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-1"></div>
        <div class="col-10">
            <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" id="nav-button-studio" href="#">Studio</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" id="nav-button-sessions" href="#">Sessions</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" id="nav-button-live" href="#">Live</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" id="nav-button-live" href="#">Talks</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="studio" class="music-listen-section">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-1"></div>
            <div id="vowel-sounds" class="col-4">
                <h4 class="text-white text-center">Vowel Sounds (Album)</h4>
                <h5 class="text-white text-center">Released September 2023</h5>

                <iframe style="width: 100%; height: 472px;"
                        src="https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=1063602042/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=0687f5/artwork=small/transparent=true/"
                        seamless><a href="/music/vowl-sounds">Vowel Sounds by Justin
                    Holmes</a></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="col-2"></div>
            <div id="nanny-state-fiddler" class="col-4">
                <h4 class="text-white text-center">Nanny State
                    Fiddler (single)</h4>
                <h5 class="text-white text-center">Released July 2022</h5>
                <iframe style="border: 0; width: 100%; height: 470px;"
                        src="https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=2958184754/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=0687f5/tracklist=false/track=3837192687/transparent=true/"
                        seamless><a href="https://justinholmes.bandcamp.com/album/nanny-state-fiddler-single">Nanny
                    State
                    Fiddler (single) by Justin Holmes</a></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="col-1"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="sessions" class="music-listen-section" style="display: none;">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-1"></div>
            <div class="col-8">
                <h3>Intimate recordings at studios or homes, with live audiences of 10 or less.</h3>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-1"></div>
            <div class="col-4">
                <h4 class="text-white text-center">Drowsy Maggie w/ David Grier</h4>
                <h5 class="text-white text-center">April 2, 2024</h5>
                <h5 class="text-white text-center">Nashville, TN</h5>
                <iframe class="w-100" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yTI1HoFYbE0?si=FXMUSny_Q3Hc3KO-"
                        title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0"
                        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                        referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="col-2"></div>
            <div class="col-4">
                <h4 class="text-white text-center">"See Each Other"</h4>
                <h5 class="text-white text-center">June 15, 20224</h5>
                <h5 class="text-white text-center">St. Pete, FLN</h5>
                <iframe class="w-100" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/l2ptKjqV4BA?si=Y5SPjyHwREZTAKZV"
                        title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0"
                        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                        referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="live" class="music-listen-section" style="display: none;">
        <h3>Recordings from live performances at venues, festivals, and events.</h3>
        <h4>I've been blessed to play my music and relay my hopes for the future of the internet all over the world,
            from Nashville to Cape Town to Osaka to Prague.</h4>
    </div>

    <div id="ensemble-intro" class="fs-4 text-start">
        <p><em>
            "After we're done with the music, it's gone. Why shouldn't they take it home with them?" - Jerry Garcia
        </em>
        </p>
        <p>
            All of my music is released under a Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-SA 4.0)
            license. Feel free to distribute, remix, and do whatever pleases you with this music, as long as you
            attribute the creators.

            You can listen to it via legacy platforms like spotify and bandcamp (and, at your discretion, purchase my
            albums from various platforms if you want to support me in this way).

            I also encourage listeners to share my music via bit torrent, IPFS, or their censorship-resistant file
            sharing platform of choice.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

